Source: openmediavault-backup
Section: misc
XB-Plugin-Section: backup
Priority: optional
Maintainer: OpenMediaVault Plugin Developers <plugins@omv-extras.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 14), dh-sequence-single-binary
Standards-Version: 4.7.2
Homepage: http://omv-extras.org/

Package: openmediavault-backup
Architecture: all
Depends: fsarchiver,
         openmediavault (>=7.7.6),
         borgbackup,
         rsync,
         fdisk,
         zstd
Description: backup plugin for OpenMediaVault.
 This plugin will backup the entire OpenMediaVault
 system minus data drives or system drive for
 restoration in emergency situations.
